																			Tags
   tags are used to define the structure and content of a webpage.
   	Syntax : <tag-name> content </tag-name>
   
   Notes : 
      * Some tags close themselves. 
      * An HTML element is defined by Tag.
      * The HTML element is everything from the start tag to the end tag.
      * Some HTML elements have no content. These elements are called empty elements.
      * Some HTML elements will display correctly, even if you forget the end tag. ( paragraph )
      * HTML is not case sensitive.
      * lorem (N) : in case you want to use some predefined paragraphs.
      
      

          
         










